// brunch.dishes → [{ name: 'Eggs', calories: 450 }, { name: 'Toast', calories: 100 }]
```

**calculateCalories(meal)** — returns `"[type] has a total of [sum] calories."`
```js
calculateCalories(brunch); // "brunch has a total of 550 calories."
```

